title: Cosmos.Ep3.The Harmony of Worlds.divx
description:
Episode 3: The Harmony of Worlds

Historical re-creation of the life and time of Johannes Kepler - the last scientific astrologer, the first modern astronomer, and the author of the first science fiction novel. Kepler provided the insight of how the moon and the planets move in their orbits and ultimately how to journey to them.

Audio: 6 Channel Stereo (English)
Video: 4:3  640x480 (Divx)
